---
title: Sautéed Shrimp with Cheddar Grits and Garlicky Collard Greens
description: Shrimp and grits is one of the most iconic Southern dishes. There are countless variations, but ours incorporates another Southern staple: collard greens! This unique veggie is often given a bad rep when prepared incorrectly – but a quick sauté with garlic is all it needs to shine!
image: https://img.hellofresh.com/f_auto,fl_lossy,h_640,q_auto,w_1200/hellofresh_s3/image/saute-ed-shrimp-857bd7db.jpg
